Package org.wmn4j.notation.elements

Class Clef

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wmn4j.notation.elements.Clef
  • public final class Clef
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a clef. Clefs have a symbol which tells the shape of the clef and position which is the line on which the center of the clef is situated. For example, the center of a G-symbol clef is the part of the clef that denotes G4.
